friends still in kuwait by car telephones that work on the other 
side of the border those inside kuwait say they are not permitted 
to buy anything in large quantities 
irans islamic republic news agency quoted iranians returning 
from kuwait as saying foodstuffs were scarce the city bazaar was 
closed and the general situation in kuwait was tense 
they say iraqi soldiers are taking position here and there 
throughout kuwait and especially in alahmadi port with tanks and 
armored vehicles roaming in the city streets amid sporadic 
overnight shooting the agency reported 
the agency estimated that 10000 iranians of the 100000strong 
iranian community in kuwait have returned to iran 
