environmental resources says the title dispute must be resolved 
first a status hearing has been scheduled for aug 30 
the department is still trying to find surveyors willing to 
brave the monkeys and measure the property plante said 
meanwhile the company is quietly scouting out alternative sites 
where the breeding operation can be moved said barbara kelley a 
spokeswoman at bausch and lombs rochester ny headquarters 
