asian organized crime groups are spreading 
into this country along with a brisk trade in heroin and soon could 
be double the size of the cosa nostra in its heyday a senate 
chairman said tuesday 
asian triads will be the dominant organized crime force in 
this country by the middle of this decade chairman joseph r 
