imported by traditional mobsters from the processing mills of 
marseilles has created a market opening for even purer shipments 
from southeast asia 
the heroin much of it coming from a rebel army based in the 
jungles of burma is shipped to singapore and taiwan and from there 
to seattle and vancouver bryant said he said most of it goes from 
there to new york for distribution throughout the country 
since 1985 southeast asian heroin as a percentage of all heroin 
seizures in the united states has increased from 14 percent to 43 
percent bryant said he said purity has increased from 3 percent 
to 5 percent in the early 1980s to 40 percent to 50 percent in 
major east coast cities now 
the bulk of the heroin enters the united states as seemingly 
legitimate cargo fbi officials said they said the traditional 
silence of the triads and the fear of retribution from them has 
