<TEXT>
saudi and iraqi pilots are playing 
catandmouse games along the border virtually every day the 
commander of a saudi air base said tuesday 
prince turki bin nasser also confirmed that the iraqis have 
moved mobile missile launchers capable of delivering chemical 
weapons into kuwait 
in the aerial games neither side is very close turki said 
normally the iraqis fly about 40 miles from the border while the 
saudis are about 20 to 30 miles from their border 
turki briefed reporters on condition they not identify the 
location of the base or the names of saudi pilots who are working 
with american fliers 
there is always this catandmouse thing on the border 
