said i wish there was as much concern for them i saw some 
pictures on television this morning of the new hostages lying 
around swimming pools for me thats not hostaging hostages to me 
is deprivation cruelty dehumanization of people 
hell they arent chained they arent blindfolded they can 
walk around there wouldnt be any comparison as far as their 
treatment they can see their captives they know whos got them 
we never could see anybody 
state department spokesman richard boucher said he would have no 
comment on reeds remarks 
reed 57 was released last april 30 after 44 months in 
captivity in lebanon he said he was chained blindfolded badly 
beaten malnourished and poisoned with arsenic he tried to escape 
twice 
